data.description: APPRAISAL IS IN!!! Fantastic home located in the heart of North Columbus. This is a 3 bed, 2 bath home that has plenty of living room and dining room space. There's an additional room that can be used as office space or playroom. The back deck is very spacious and would be great for hosting. Very convenient to JR Allen PKWY, 185, Bradley Park, etc. This property qualifies for a seller credit of $10,000 towards buyer's closing costs or interest rate buy downs. Buyer is not obligated to use The Z team of Cross Country Mortgage to have offer accepted, however must use The Z Team to qualify for the credit.  Home has foundation issue(s) please see attached documents. Seller is willing to fix what is necessary for serious buyer(s). See attachment for appraisal report. Door code located in private remarks.
